      • getReferenceFeature

        public Feature getReferenceFeature(Feature feature)
                            throws DAOException
        Retrieve the Feature object for the given Feature object. Since only one Feature object should exist for a given unique sequence, this method is used to prevent creation of duplicate features.

        Use this to look for a reference feature that should exist in the features table, such as known biobrick prefix/suffix/scar sequence. This method creates the feature if it doesn't exist, using the values passed.

        Parameters:
        feature -
        Returns:
        Feature object.
        Throws:
        DAOException
